OpenContainingFolder

Adds an option to open the folder containing the selected track(s) to 
the right click context menu.


=== Dependencies ===

  * rhythmbox		    >= 	2.97
  * pygtk/gobject
  * xdg-utils


=== Usage ===

To install, run 'install.sh' or copy the 'OpenContainingFolder' directory 
and its contents to ~/.local/share/rhythmbox/plugins/.


=== Thanks ===

Partly based on rb-open-folder by Adolfo González Blázquez.


